00102 void DeJongFunction::setNumberOfVariables(int newNumberOfVariables)
00103 {
00104    numberOfVariables = newNumberOfVariables;
00105 
00106    // Set multilayer perceptron stuff
00107 
00108    multilayerPerceptron->setNumberOfIndependentParameters(numberOfVariables);
00109    
00110    for(int i = 0; i < numberOfVariables; i++)
00111    {
00112       std::stringstream buffer;
00113       buffer << "x" << i+1;
00114       multilayerPerceptron->setNameOfSingleIndependentParameter(i, buffer.str());
00115 
00116       multilayerPerceptron->setMinimumOfSingleIndependentParameter(i, -5.12);
00117       multilayerPerceptron->setMaximumOfSingleIndependentParameter(i, 5.12);  
00118    }
00119 
00120    multilayerPerceptron->initIndependentParametersUniform(-5.12, 5.12);
